   Kennedy, Elizabeth M.; Mildenhall, Dallas C., GNS Sci, POB 30368, Lower Hutt 5040, New Zealand.
   Lee, Daphne E., Univ Otago, Dept Geol, POB 56, Dunedin 9054, New Zealand.},
